0.code:
N = 4
K = 145
A = [2, 3, 1, 4]
i=A.index(1)+1
if i<=K or i>=N-K:
    ans=(N-K)//(K-1)+1 if (N-K)%(K-1)==0 else (N-K)//(K-1)+2
else:
    for a in range(K):
        b=0 if (i-a)%(K-1)==0 and (N-(i+(K-a)))%(K-1)==0 else 1
    front=i//(K-1)
    back=(N-(i+K))//(K-1)
    ans=front+back+1+b
print(ans)

K = 1522
A = [2, 3, 1, 4]

    ans=(N-K)//(K-1)+1 if (N-K)%(K-1)==0 else (N-K)//(K-1)+2
else:
    for a in range(K):
        b=0 if (i-a)%(K-1)==0 and (N-(i+(K-a)))%(K-1)==0 else 1
    front=i//(K-1)
    back=(N-(i+K))//(K-1)
    ans=front+back+1+b
print(ans)

K = 374
A = [2, 3, 1, 4]
i=A.index(1)+1
if i<=K or i>=N-K:
    ans=(N-K)//(K-1)+1 if (N-K)%(K-1)==0 else (N-K)//(K-1)+2
else:
    for a in range(K):
        b=0 if (i-a)%(K-1)==0 and (N-(i+(K-a)))%(K-1)==0 else 1
    front=i//(K-1)
    back=(N-(i+K))//(K-1)
    ans=front+back+1+b
print(ans)

K = 369
A = [2, 3, 1, 4]
i=A.index(1)+1
if i<=K or i>=N-K:
    ans=(N-K)//(K-1)+1 if (N-K)%(K-1)==0 else (N-K)//(K-1)+2
else:
    for a in range(K):
        b=0 if (i-a)%(K-1)==0 and (N-(i+(K-a)))%(K-1)==0 else 1
    front=i//(K-1)
    back=(N-(i+K))//(K-1)
    ans=front+back+1+b
print(ans)
